<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1606009002">
<title>
Radiator Cooling Fan Motor
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect radiator cooling fan motor connector (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70P160004.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "65.899mm" ver = "01" gw = "201" gh = "170"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using service wire, connect radiator cooling fan motor connector and battery as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A160002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.839mm" ver = "01" gw = "222" gh = "122"/>
