<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that radiator cooling fan motors rotate smoothly and properly.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If any abnormality is found, replace radiator cooling fan motor.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Reference: Fan motor specified current at 12 V
</title>
<ptxt>
Low speed: 4.8 – 7.8 A
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
High speed: 7.4 – 10.9 A
</ptxt>
